            "properties": {},
            "widgets_values": [
                "# FrameWeaver Post-Processing Demo\n\nThis workflow demonstrates the post-processing chain without any LTX generation. It works with any image batch.\n\n**Pipeline:** Load images → FW_ColorMatch (match to reference) → FW_CinematicPolish (sharpen) → FW_FilmGrain (add texture) → FW_LUTApply (color grade) → Save\n\n**Tips:** Adjust FW_CinematicPolish mode (unsharp/laplacian/sobel) and strength. Start FW_FilmGrain at 0.25 intensity. Use FW_LUTCreate to generate custom .cube LUTs from hex palettes."
            ]
        },
